        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This is the updated version of the <a href="https://mdai-econ.com/post/third-party-certification-1/">previous writing sample</a> and was also my Master's thesis. The model has been much improved, along with more detailed illustrating. That being said, there's still a lot of space for this model to become better and I am working on this. The new English version of this paper is expected to have a draft before summer, 2024.</p>
<p>Also, you can click <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1r85uussiKoXu1MK3eip_1IW06s4aLIzr/view?usp=sharing">here</a> for the access to the pdf <em>OR</em> <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1n5Qbz8qg4_kWXwn4GBIDqShKfiQ5Eolq/view?usp=sharing">here</a> for the access to the version <strong>with notes</strong>. (Links to Google Drive)<br>
Copyright reserved. If you want the access to the pdf of the <strong>paper</strong> (in Chinese), please email <a href="mailto:academic@mdai-econ.com">Mingzhao DAI</a>.</p>
